/var @name = "World"

/run {echo "Hello @name"}
/run "echo 'hello name'"
/exe @step1(var) = "echo 'hello @var'"

=== START TOKENS ===
@name --> variable[declaration]
= --> operator
"World" --> string
{ --> operator
} --> operator
echo --> string
@name --> variable
@step1 --> variable[declaration]
( --> operator
var) --> parameter
) --> operator
= --> operator
@var --> variable
